{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"56ca1370f2","title":"关于筹款的训令","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f7e95b264d","index":0,"year":1936,"month":8,"day":18,"articleId":"56ca1370f2"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"41377a5526","type":"paragraph","text":"关于筹款的训令","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"56ca1370f2"},{"id":"7df8a95940","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年8月18日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"56ca1370f2"},{"id":"4b48c76f78","type":"paragraph","text":"根据最近中央对于土地政策的新决定，对于地主，只要他不反对抗日红军，应避免用没收办法，而以捐募的方法使其尽量拿出金钱、粮食和物品，宁可少没收一家，不可错没收一家。在筹款中，必须注意经济政策，没收地主的商店固然不对，没收一般的商店无不容许。在苏维埃法律范围内，给商人以适当的保护。在不损害商业的条件下，向富商作深入的救国宣传，进行募捐运动，筹得抗日经费。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"56ca1370f2"},{"id":"44ca2321d3","type":"paragraph","text":"[11这是西北革命军事委员会主席毛泽东和副主席周恩来、彭德怀，政治部主任杨尚昆，中央财政部长林伯渠联名发布的关于筹款的训令。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"56ca1370f2"}],"page":{"id":"1d11f809b2","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"56ca1370f2","start":77,"end":77}}}},"__N_SSG":true}